{"type": "article", "id": 49542, "title": "亚马逊提高服饰类卖家门槛，以及，Balenciaga 的老爸鞋产自中国 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-24T04:01:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 2881, "name": "Vera Wang"}, {"id": 38371, "name": "Wedgwood"}, {"id": 29383, "name": "Sandro"}, {"id": 3968, "name": "P&G"}, {"id": 321, "name": "Amazon"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/201801241146409YkP84wItXjEQFRs.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-raises-seller-fees-for-apparel-and-accessories-2018-1\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>亚马逊提高服饰类卖家门槛</strong></a> | 除调高 Prime 会员费以外，亚马逊还同时调高了服装品类第三方卖家需要缴纳的佣金——服装配饰类从 15% 调到 17%，手袋墨镜类对定价 75 美元以上的商品从 15% 调到 18%。有分析说这种做法可能是为了遏制山寨卖家，吸引高端品牌入驻。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/01/23/procter-gamble-earnings-q2-2018.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>宝洁发布 2018 第二季度财报，业绩略高于预期</strong></a> | 宝洁财报显示，过去三个月内集团的销售额同比增长 3%，至 174.4 亿美元，略高于此前预期的 173.9 亿美元。受降价策略影响，业绩略有上涨，但毛利率大跌了 68%，至 25 亿美元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>在前几天的 COMME des GARÇONS HOMME PLUS 秀场上，品牌发布了一双与 melissa 合作的鞋子还蛮特别的。</p><p>这双鞋共有黑白两种颜色，运用了 melissa 特有的 mono block 技术，因而鞋身没有针脚。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113850DYdLnqisfakhBZru.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.847458\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113850hJj38uasRkXF1n0y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.865152\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113857wzdBafmbiOQUXHVF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.865152\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801241138589iJGRZsOWFaYdkqh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.865152\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113850gH1PGEVvzhK5RBs9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.866129\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113857pEMerX0qjn15xADJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.865152\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113857K9DAxJdNW2HGszyP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.865152\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>做婚纱的 <a href=\"https://popbee.com/lifestyle/home-and-living/vera-wang-wedgwood-2018-dinnerware-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vera Wang</a> 和英国瓷器品牌 Wedgwood 的最新联名，推出了以花为灵感、设计简约的餐具系列。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113642J9r8RCToXwYq7MID.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113642bLhxA6XdUO8fTuSp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113642AEg7MmQY1W3bOJiS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113643g5JQRNqzcr6iwtuZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>伦敦泰特美术馆最近在举办一场以旧苏联文化为主题的展览，名为<a href=\"https://casabrutus.com/design/65469\" rel=\"nofollow\">“俄罗斯的红星·视觉文化的革命”展。 </a></p><p>展品来自已故收藏家 David King 的收藏以及泰特美术馆购买的近 25000 件藏品，时间范围从 1905 年开始，到斯大林逝世之后的 1955 年，囊括了特殊政治背景下的海报、印刷物、写真等。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113626rJNvVXckd3yFl8xj.png\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/1/balenciaga-triple-s-made-in-china\" rel=\"nofollow\">Balenciaga 证实，已把 Triple S 的生产线转移到中国。 </a></p><p>之前有 Reddit 用户吐槽说，Balenciaga 鞋子的质量越来越差了，因为他发现他买到的鞋子是 Made in China 的。 </p><p>Balenciaga 回应说，Triple S 最初是在意大利制造的，但是最近被转移到了中国，因为那里有足够的资格和能力生产出更轻的鞋子。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113615gQskfUnz7MNOYqIB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-2018/paris/sandro/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sandro 发布 2018 秋冬系列</a>，用了不少灯芯绒元素，一如既往地，还不错。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113522badGHR4STpCeN5mi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113522dckgxO1mHfeX6C58.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113523dKYAgaNeZqbusjPz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801241135230hfW7atpbS3kGZvA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113524HyikdOXfsbW3jFgm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113524yOcQJkh7qjpwXt4s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113524eKZtIrbh9pjMVBul.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113525LmYprhuBwjv9cEAe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113526YyrBJGue4OV9fFq0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113527ExwYZRTyUlJPk9iQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113528TPE7p8NVAKWXxOva.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113529sCfXIuZvb367okBW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113529n9j7TFBqDtfLH8WR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113529ZQR1XmMUHiqrkjCB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113529EWYaJAV12vfU6DCj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113529Lzix4skDBr3fWv8d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113530VM4SYcsz70912Wod.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113530Lr9IxovJbnGkTw02.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>时隔八年，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/spring-couture-2018/paris/givenchy/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Givenchy</a> 在新创意总监 Clare Waight Keller 的带领下，重回巴黎高定时装周。 </p><p>在大秀结束后的后台，Clare 称，“这是属于老灵魂的新轮回”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113440fFU0BZ4iu8TP3bjJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113443nquQTvNZCJ93Ubwe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113443xsyFhJHYCacX8Mew.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801241134452y3aAjdQLW6YgPsZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113446iQhcTSrmDvsWCZ62.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113446WXzjftoORGemHUKc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113447j5QAEFCchxd0Sswz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801241134489yBhic68fkUCrm0u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113448u3UlJOErTCIKgqyW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113451a75JdyqK2XQEYmtw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113451YM10ARb3VQJFPODf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113450fj3N48QdiSkZ6IBw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113451KEVfsXRyJtIQMZ26.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113452Ume7BXldzsoIk6Cw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113453tG8S4xjHp3wQeg5h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113453X9df2JpKQiwOAT6h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180124113454DFduY8GlhX76pego.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Givenchy</p>"}